name: Yummy Yum Cha
effect: Restores 14% of Max HP to the selected character and regenerates 350 HP every 5s for 30s.
description: Gaming's specialty. Row upon row of lifelike suanni buns sit pretty within the steamer, bringing the formidable, clever youth leaping amidst the Plum Blossom Pole... "What's with that dumbfounded expression? Have a cup of tea first, eh?" With that, the cheerfully smiling fellow passes you another cup.
